title: Denmark Car Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Denmark decreased to 10895 in October from 13056 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Denmark averaged 10746.99  from 1960 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 29700  in May of 1997 and a record low of 1191  in December of 1974. This page provides - Denmark Car Registrations - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Denmark
